OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry but
OL,6,Fprobably rather cloudy, the best of
OL,7,Fany breaks in the evening with some
OL,8,Fsunny spells possible. Winds light or
OL,9,Fmoderate from the north.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FStaying dry and mostly cloudy,
OL,12,Fbut some bright spells with the cloud
OL,13,Fexpected to break at times. Feeling
OL,14,Fcool and fresh at times with light to
OL,15,Fmoderate north or northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
