OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and settled, although a little
OL,7,Fearly light rain or drizzle possible.
OL,8,FOften cloudy, but skies brightening
OL,9,Fwith occasional sunny spells. Feeling
OL,10,Ffresh, moderate north or northwest
OL,11,Fwinds.
